  <brief_title>Randomized, Double-blind, Two Arms, Multicenter, Phase III Study of Berinert for Treatment of ACE Induced Angioedema</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized, Double-blind, Two Arms, Multicenter, Phase III Study of Berinert for Treatment of ACE Induced Angioedema</official_title>
